It can also be a constant.

1446
01:28:20,460 --> 01:28:22,560
Yeah, yeah.

1447
01:28:32,520 --> 01:28:36,000
So question is, is
there a relation

1448
01:28:36,000 --> 01:28:38,160
with explore and exploit?

