01:29:14,120 --> 01:29:15,153
Exactly, yes.

1460
01:29:15,153 --> 01:29:16,820
So I'm not sure if
this was super clear,

1461
01:29:16,820 --> 01:29:18,112
but this is actually the label.

1462
01:29:18,112 --> 01:29:21,910
So what you're trying to
predict is not 1, 0, 0.

1463
01:29:21,910 --> 01:29:26,450
But we change the label in
